Brett Peter Cowan was convicted of murdering 13-year-old Daniel Morcombe in December 2003 .
He was sentenced to life in prison for murdering and dumping the body of the Sunshine Coast teenager .
Cowan's barrister Peter Davis said he met with Bravehearts founder Hetty Johnson and included a smiley face .
Corkan's sentence includes a non-parole period of 20 years .